* Fri Jul 19 2024 Mohammed Isam <mohammed_isam1984@yahoo.com> 2.0-1
- Bugfixes
- Reformatted the whole codebase and removed redundant code
- The library depends on ncurses now for better portability
- Renamed show_readme() to showReadme() to match codebase naming
- Renamed show_about() to showAbout() to match codebase naming
- showReadme() accepts a FILE handle now instead of a path
- Removed catchAllSignals() and catchSignals()
- Button types macros are now prefixed with BUTTON_ due to clashes
  with some ncurses macros (e.g. OK is now BUTTON_OK)
- Unicode support - corelib, prime and mino now use widechars internally
  to support non-Latin letters

